            <h2 style={{ margin: '0.25rem 0 0', color: '#fff' }}>Department Orders</h2>
            <p style={{ margin: '0.4rem 0 0', color: '#94a3b8', fontSize: '0.875rem' }}>Choose a focused order for each staff room.</p>
